ork City, till Exit 14(Nanuet). At the 1st light make left turn onto Rt.59(E). At 4th light (before Exxon Gas Station) turn right onto MiddleTown Rd., then pass 5 traffic lights. Church is on your left.</li><br />\r\n\t<li><u>Take Garden State Parkway N</u><br />\r\n\tFrom Garden St. Parkway through NY Thruway to Exit Nanuet, to Rt. 59(E)., At 4th light (before Exxon Gas Station) turn right onto MiddleTown Rd., then pass 5 traffic lights. Church is on your left. </li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>\r\n<b><i>By BUS</i></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 Take bus #11A and get off at North Middle Town Rd. across the street from the pharmaceutical office in Pearl River. \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<b><i>By TRAIN</i></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 Pearl River is also accessible via the Pascack Valley train from Hoboken, NJ. \r\n</p>\r\n'));          
