\u540d\u7684\u5f1f\u5144\u59ca\u59b9\u53ca\u670b\u53cb\u5011\u6e96\u6642\u51fa\u5e2d\uff0c\u4e26\u70ba\u672a\u4fe1\u4e3b\u7684\u670b\u53cb\u5011\u4ee3\u79b1\u3002</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt\" lang=\"NL\">Morgenavond, 12\r\nseptember wordt het midherfstfeest gehouden. De kerk is open om 17:30 uur, het\r\nfeest begint om 18:00 uur. Willen broeders, zusters en vrienden, die aangemeld\r\nhebben op tijd aanwezig te zijn en graag voor de niet-gelovige vrienden te\r\nbidden.</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt\" lang=\"NL\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 13pt\">\r\n<b><span style=\"font-size: 11pt\" lang=\"NL\">\u00a0</span></b>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 13pt\">\r\n<b><span style=\"font-size: 11pt\" lang=\"NL\">4. </span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: ''PMingLiU'',''serif''\" lang=\"ZH-TW\">\u656c\u8001\u4e3b\u65e5</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: ''PMingLiU'',''serif''\" lang=\"ZH-TW\">\uff1a</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt\" lang=\"NL\">Seniorendag</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 13pt\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: ''PMingLiU'',''serif''\" lang=\"ZH-TW\">\u4e5d\u6708\u7684\u7b2c\u4e09\u500b\u4e3b\u65e5</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt\" lang=\"NL\">( 9<span style=\"font-family: ''PMingLiU'',''serif''\" lang=\"ZH-TW\">\u6708</span>18<span style=\"font-family: ''PMingLiU'',''serif''\" lang=\"ZH-TW\">\u65e5</span> )</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: ''PMingLiU'',''serif''\" lang=\"ZH-TW\">\u5b9a\u70ba\u656c\u8001\u4e3b\u65e5\uff0c\u85c9\u7740\u9019\u4e00\u5e74\u4e00\u5ea6\u7684\u656c\u8001\u4e3b\u65e5\uff0c\u63d0\u9192\u5e74\u8f15\u7684\u5f1f\u5144\u59ca\u59b9\u8981\u656c\u8001\uff0c\u9019\u662f\u8056\u7d93\u7684\u6559\u8a13\uff0c\u66f4\u91cd\u8981\u7684\u662f\u5c07\u798f\u97f3\u50b3\u7d66\u672a\u4fe1\u4e3b\u7684\u7236\u6bcd\u548c\u89aa\u53cb\uff0c\u8b93\u4ed6</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt\" lang=\"NL\">(</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: ''PMingLiU'',''serif''\" lang=\"ZH-TW\">\u5979</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt\" lang=\"NL\">)</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: ''PMingLiU'',''serif''\" lang=\"ZH-TW\">\u5011\u6709\u6a5f\u6703\u807d\u805e\u798f\u97f3\uff0c\u4e26\u63a5\u53d7\u6551\u6069\uff0c\u8aa0\u8acb\u5f1f\u5144\u59ca\u59b9\u9080\u8acb\u89aa\u53cb\u53c3\u52a0\u9019\u6b21\u798f\u97f3\u6027\u805a\u6703\uff0c\u4e26\u70ba\u8a72\u5929\u7684\u805a\u6703\u4ee3\u79b1\u3002</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt\" lang=\"NL\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 12pt\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 11pt\" lang=\"NL\">Op de derde zondag van september, 18 september 2011,\r\nwordt de seniorendag gehouden. Dat de jongere broeders en zusters door deze\r\njaarlijkse seniorendag eraan herinnerd mogen worden respect te hebben voor\r\nouderen. Nog belangrijker is om het evangelie aan de niet gelovige ouders en\r\nvrienden te vertellen. Dat ze een kans mogen hebben om het evangelie te horen\r\nen te accepteren. Willen broeders en zusters hun familie en vrienden uitnodigen\r\nvoor deze evangelische bijeenkomst en ook voor deze dag bidden.</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 13pt\">\r\n<b><span style=\"font-size: 11pt\" lang=\"NL\">\u00a0</span></b>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 13pt\">\r\n<b><span style=\"font-size: 11pt\" lang=\"NL\">5</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: ''PMingLiU'',''serif''\" lang=\"NL\">. </span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: ''PMingLiU'',''serif''\" lang=\"ZH-TW\">\u6b61\u8fce\u65b0\u670b\u53cb</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: ''PMingLiU'',''serif''\" lang=\"ZH-TW\">\uff1a</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt\" lang=\"NL\">Verwelkoming:</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: ''PMingLiU'',''serif''\" lang=\"NL\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 13pt\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: ''PMingLiU'',''serif''\" lang=\"ZH-TW\">\u975e\u5e38\u6b61\u8fce\u4e0a\u661f\u671f\u7b2c\u4e00\u6b21\u5230\u672c\u6703\u53c3\u52a0\u805a\u6703\u3002</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: ''PMingLiU'',''serif''\" lang=\"ZH-TW\">\u5289\u5c11\u6c11\u592b\u5a66\u3001\u90ed\u6bb7\u59ca\u59b9\u3001\u5289\u8a60\u99a8\u59ca\u59b9\u3001\u9ec3\u6c38\u5065\u5148\u751f\u3001\u90b1\u88d5\u83ef\u5f1f\u5144\u3001\u738b\u6377\u5c0f\u59d0\u3001</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: ''Tahoma'',''sans-serif''\" lang=\"ZH-TW\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: ''PMingLiU'',''serif''\" lang=\"ZH-TW\">\u59da\u71be\u6b23\u5c0f\u59d0\u3001\u8881\u66f8\u5a55\u5c0f\u59d0</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: ''PMingLiU'',''serif''\" lang=\"ZH-TW\">\u3002</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: ''Tahoma'',''sans-serif''\" lang=\"NL\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 13pt\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 11pt\" lang=\"NL\">We verwelkomen degenen die vorige week onze\r\nzondagsdienst voor het eerst hadden bijgewoond. </span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: ''PMingLiU'',''serif''\" lang=\"NL\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 11pt\" lang=\"NL\">komen degenen die vorige week onze zondagsdienst voor het eerst hadden\r\nbijgewoond. </span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 13pt\">\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 10pt\" lang=\"NL\"></span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: ''PMingLiU'',''serif''\" lang=\"NL\"></span>\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 11pt\" lang=\"NL\"></span><u1:smarttagtype namespaceuri=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:smarttags\" name=\"time\"></u1:smarttagtype><b><span style=\"font-family: ''PMingLiU'',''serif''\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: ''PMingLiU'',''serif''\" lang=\"NL\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b>\r\n'));    
