family: \u65b0\u7d30\u660e\u9ad4; font-size: 10pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"color: #000000\">2002\u5e743\u670810\u65e5\u300c\u99ac\u5fb7\u91cc\u57fa\u7763\u6559\u751f\u547d\u5802\u300d\u516d\u9031\u5e74\u6176\u66a8\u737b\u5802\u3002<o:p></o:p></span></span><span style=\"font-family: \u65b0\u7d30\u660e\u9ad4; font-size: 10pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"color: #000000\">2004\u5e744\u670818\u65e5\u674e\u6708\u96f2\u50b3\u9053\u6309\u7acb\u7267\u5e2b\u3002<o:p></o:p></span></span> \r\n<h2 style=\"line-height: 20pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; background: white; tab-stops: 285.3pt 296.15pt\"><span style=\"font-family: \u65b0\u7d30\u660e\u9ad4; color: #333333; font-size: 10pt\">\u73fe\u70ba\u897f\u73ed\u7259\u798f\u97f3\u4f48\u9053\u6703\u6703\u7267<span lang=\"EN-US\">, \u99ac\u5fb7\u91cc\u57fa\u7763\u6559\u751f\u547d\u5802\u4e3b\u4efb\u7267\u5e2b</span></span><span style=\"font-family: \u65b0\u7d30\u660e\u9ad4; font-size: 10pt\"><span style=\"color: #000000\">\u3002</span></span><span style=\"font-family: ''Times New Roman''; color: #333333; font-size: 14.5pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n'));              
INSERT INTO PUBLIC.CHURCH_CONTENT(CHURCH_ID, PAGE_ID, LOCALE, TITLE, BODY) VALUES(27, 'news', 'en', 'CEC in Madrid - Latest News', STRINGDECODE('<h2 style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; font-weight: normal; font-family: Arial,MingLiU,Helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 21px; line-height: 25pt; background-color: white; padding: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \u6a19\u6977\u9ad4; color: black\">(This page is in spanish - \u8fd9\u9875\u662f\u7528\u897f\u73ed\u7259\u8bed\u5199\u7684 - Esta p\u00e1gina est\u00e1 en espa\u00f1ol)</span></h2>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n\t<li><span style=\"font-size: small\" class=\"Apple-style-span\">Los s\u00e1bados a las 19:15 y los domingos tras el Culto Dominical, el coro grande ensayar\u00e1 la canci\u00f3n para la Semana Santa. </span></li>\r\n\t<li><span style=\"font-size: small\" class=\"Apple-style-span\">El \u00faltimo domingo de mes, despu\u00e9s del Culto, se celebrar\u00e1 una cena preparada por los hermanos o por las hermanas, turn\u00e1ndose cada mes entre ellos.</span></li>\r\n\t<li><span style=\"font-size: small\" class=\"Apple-style-span\">Cada s\u00e1bado a las 18:00 hay estudio de la Biblia. Ahora se est\u00e1 estudiando &quot;Abd\u00edas&quot;. Se anima a todos para participar en el estudio de las Sagradas Escrituras.</span></li>\r\n\t<li><span style=\"font-size: small\" class=\"Apple-style-span\">El domingo 18 de marzo, la iglesia de Madrid celebr\u00f3 su 16\u00ba aniversario.<br />\r\n\t</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n'));  
