ew Church Building \" title=\"CEC in Antwerpen\" height=\"270\" align=\"left\" hspace=\"5\" width=\"360\" />\r\n<p>\r\nThe EMSI short term mission to Belgium in the spring of 2000 covered Antwerpen and Brussels. We saw the need for the Gospel in Brussels there and established the CEC in Brussels in May 2004. We have morning service in Antwerpen and afternoon service in Brussels. God raised up godly members who came to serve with us from Antwerpen to Brussels. Their faithfulness really encouraged us greatly<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\nLeft: CEC in Antwerpen purchased a new church building. \r\n</p>\r\n</div>\r\n'));     
